Description.val: The family of 60mm mortar cartridges is designed to be fired from the M224 lightweight mortar system in support of Company sized Infantry maneuvers.  The family of munitions consists of high explosive, smoke, illumination, and full range training practice rounds.  The 60mm family of cartridges is used to provide close-in indirect fire support of ground troops at ranges of approximately 70 to 3,500 meters.

Justification.val: The funds in FY18 and out have been realigned to line item 1085.
